{"id": 1509, "genre": 1001, "title": "现如今，你觉得你的择偶标准有哪些不太传统的地方？", "description": "对于恋人的选择，你有什么独到的标准？（题图来自：Evdokiya illustrator）", "record_count": 7808, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170215173857AMCUXxoyrYcEiSDk.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-02-23T03:00:41Z", "options": [{"id": 170752, "content": "可以有钱但一定要有趣", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 946712}, {"id": 170753, "content": "和谐，性，钱，观念", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 265217}, {"id": 171009, "content": "在一起说废话也不觉得尴尬", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 945662}, {"id": 170754, "content": "真凶", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 940589}, {"id": 171010, "content": "拒绝小孩，不光看脸，还看情商", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 947389}, {"id": 170755, "content": "非真爱不妥协，三四十岁单身也没关系", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 934705}, {"id": 172291, "content": "只因为是你，无关性别，无关其他", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 947004}, {"id": 175107, "content": "三观合，在一起不尴尬", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 952379}, {"id": 170756, "content": "已放弃", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 853591}, {"id": 171268, "content": "各吃各的~", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 533967}, {"id": 171524, "content": "没父母", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 918214}, {"id": 174853, "content": "别像死鱼一样", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 892094}, {"id": 170758, "content": "投缘", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 898541}, {"id": 170503, "content": "小个子平胸", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 908230}, {"id": 170759, "content": "很多人连订婚都没呢就发生关系，是不是太随便了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 946749}, {"id": 172295, "content": "不明白为什么一定要生小孩，为自己活一辈子不好么，只有短短几十年", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 861667}, {"id": 173063, "content": "个人不喜欢太瘦的男生，看见就想避开，怕碰折了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 953918}, {"id": 170760, "content": "来啊，一起玩啊！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 946753}, {"id": 171272, "content": "不找备胎", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 948289}, {"id": 170761, "content": "真爱不分性别，偏偏同性更相互吸引", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 939355}, {"id": 170762, "content": "没人敢说他传统过，那些你懂的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 883621}, {"id": 171018, "content": "传统不一定就是好的，非传统就不一定是不好的，自由所爱就好。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 947423}, {"id": 174090, "content": "性别无所谓。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 956261}, {"id": 170763, "content": "如果一个人过得更轻松愉快，在不给家人带来额外负担压力的情况下，还是想一个人过", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 900075}, {"id": 170764, "content": "不关注生辰八字，只有情投意合！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 946762}, {"id": 171276, "content": "可于太随意", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 948315}, {"id": 171788, "content": "不一定非得结婚和生小孩", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 949252}, {"id": 175372, "content": "戴眼镜，手好看，声音好听，比我高", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 960659}, {"id": 170765, "content": "到了大学依然提醒自己不要因为寂寞在一起。你要相信缘分，总有一天他会怀着一颗热力跳动的心脏穿越汹涌的人群走向你。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 855154}, {"id": 171277, "content": "就是啊，为什么两个人认识了，就得发展到性，才行啊，", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 948315}, {"id": 170510, "content": "婚前性行为", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 929773}, {"id": 170766, "content": "能遇见一个善解人意的更好，随缘。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 946759}, {"id": 170511, "content": "性取向本身就具有流动性，怎么会有人大惊小怪。", "image": null, "praise_count": 37, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 946188}, {"id": 170767, "content": "能遇见相互包容理解的更好，随缘吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 946759}, {"id": 170512, "content": "少妇", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 931967}, {"id": 170768, "content": "有灵魂的有趣的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 945838}, {"id": 172048, "content": "三观不同的人是很难在一起的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 950408}, {"id": 170513, "content": "恋爱以后就可以啪啪啪???太快了吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 945818}, {"id": 173585, "content": "门当户对", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 954825}, {"id": 175377, "content": "不想整天在一起", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 925039}, {"id": 170770, "content": "可以不结婚", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 927523}, {"id": 170771, "content": "还是看脸。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 923429}, {"id": 170517, "content": "完全不想择偶", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 920921}, {"id": 170773, "content": "到中年再好好找个相伴到老的爱人，至于前面40年，尽情的做自己好了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 736449}, {"id": 174101, "content": "单身主义思想很好  想嗨就嗨  想找就找  有时候处对象了人的确会变成傻子  为别人改变自己  一丁点都不想！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 953036}, {"id": 174869, "content": "呃不择偶", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 958779}, {"id": 170518, "content": "不要求孝顺\n愚孝是家庭低劣之源\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 931774}, {"id": 170774, "content": "好好奇我写的那条里，另外一个点赞的人是谁", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 897194}, {"id": 171798, "content": "在没有遇到对的同性之前，总以为自己喜欢异性。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 714671}, {"id": 175638, "content": "三观不合，门不当户不对", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 961336}]}